t%20can%20really%20cheapen%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BGenerally%2C%20the%20spaces%20that%20feel%20the%20most%20luxurious%20and%20welcoming%20are%20warmer%20spaces.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224163%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20all-white%20kitchen%20with%20stainless%20steel%20appliances.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F673b7870ede4eeae39283133%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223330%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20lack%20of%20color%20in%20your%20kitchen%20can%20make%20it%20look%20cheap.%3Cp%3EJoseph%20Hendrickson%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40julianaghani%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJuliana%20Ghani%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20interior%20designer%20from%20Minneapolis%2C%20tries%20to%20avoid%20too%20much%20gray%2C%20black%2C%20white%2C%20or%20%26quot%3Banything%20that%20looks%20sterile%26quot%3B%20in%20kitchens.%20She%20said%20LED%20light%20bulbs%20are%20a%20huge%20no-no%20for%20her%20in%20particular.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20looks%20like%20an%20operating%20room%20when%20you%20have%20those%20blue%20LED%20lights%20on%20your%20island%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20warm%20lighting%20is%20%26quot%3Bthe%20easiest%20way%20to%20make%20your%20kitchen%20look%20richer%20and%20homey.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20want%20to%20bring%20more%20color%20into%20your%20kitchen%2C%20Ghani%20said%20darker%20tones%2C%20like%20aubergine%2C%20olive%20green%2C%20and%20burgundy%2C%20are%20trending%20for%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2205987bb9-07cd-4a2a-8cbe-9a504b5ccd62%5C%22%3EThe%20design%20is%20in%20the%20details%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Ghani%20told%20BI%2C%20luxury%20kitchens%20are%20designed%20to%20be%20aesthetically%20pleasing%2C%20whereas%20a%20more%20basic%20kitchen%20makes%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fdeals%2Fkitchenaid-artisan-stand-mixer-amazon-deal-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20appliances%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20focal%20point%20of%20the%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20a%20mistake%20people%20make%20when%20designing%20a%20kitchen%2C%20especially%20an%20open-concept%20kitchen%2C%20is%20that%20they%20let%20the%20appliances%20dominate%20the%20space%2C%26quot%3B%20Ghani%20said.%20%26quot%3BIn%20a%20luxury%20kitchen%2C%20we%20would%20have%20paneled%20appliances%2C%20integrated%20hardware%2C%20or%20even%20different%20finishes%20on%20the%20actual%20appliances%20that%20kind%20of%20hide%20them%20in%20a%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20row%20of%20stainless%20steel%20appliances%2C%20pretty%20much%2C%20is%20not%20giving%20luxury%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224108%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20kitchen%20with%20white%20cabinets%20and%20simple%20silver%20hardware.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682e095368a292900801eead%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223081%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAppliances%20shouldn't%20define%20your%20kitchen.%3Cp%3EJoe%20Hendrickson%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEustace%20agreed%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20details%20of%20a%20kitchen%20can%20make%20a%20big%20difference%20to%20how%20your%20eye%20perceives%20the%20overall%20space.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20handles%20you%20choose%20for%20your%20cabinets%2C%20the%20stone%20you%20select%20for%20your%20countertops%2C%20or%20even%20the%20outlet%20panels%20you%20use%20can%20make%20the%20space%20feel%20less%20luxurious.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20kitchen%20can%20be%20really%20nice%2C%20and%20then%20if%20I%20see%20cup%20handles%20or%20something%2C%20immediately%20I'm%20just%20like%2C%20'Oh%20gosh%2C%20that%20really%20just%20cheapens%20the%20whole%20feel%20of%20it%2C'%26quot%3B%20Eustace%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20curved%20handles%20that%20don't%20look%20high-end.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUpgrading%20your%20hardware%20is%20an%20easy%20way%20to%20give%20your%20kitchen%20a%20luxurious%20feel%2C%20though.%20Ghani%20recommends%20brushed%20chrome%2C%20brushed%20nickel%2C%20or%20lacquered%20brass.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222de7866a-731c-44e7-bdf9-1960d4e2ebe8%5C%22%3EToo%20much%20on%20the%20counters%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGhani%20said%20that%20too%20many%20items%20on%20your%20counters%20can%20look%20%26quot%3Bmessy%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bcluttered.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20flip%20side%2C%20cookbooks%20or%20appliances%20you%20use%20daily%20on%20your%20countertops%20can%20help%20a%20space%20look%20lived%20in.%20Eustace%20agreed%2C%20saying%20you%20don't%20want%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkitchen-designs-that-dont-age-well-according-to-interior-designers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eyour%20kitchen%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20look%20uninviting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20there's%20an%20obsession%20these%20days%20with%20having%20everything%20hidden%2C%20as%20if%20it's%20like%20a%20showroom%20the%20whole%20time%20and%20no%20one%20lives%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20Eustace%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20people%20should%20be%20afraid%20to%20have%20things%20out%20or%2C%20you%20know%2C%20have%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20mess%20or%20clutter.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThings%20that%20you're%20actually%20using%20every%20day%2C%20and%20just%20signs%20of%20life%2C%20don't%20make%20it%20look%20cheap%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added%2C%20though%20she%20said%20microwaves%20sitting%20on%20a%20counter%20aren't%20aesthetically%20pleasing%20in%20her%20opinion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kitchen%20appliances%20sitting%20on%20a%20brown%20countertop.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F665f2f72cc442a2f676dc065%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKitchen%20appliances%20sitting%20out%20can%20look%20cheap.%3Cp%3EPixel-Sh