nistry%20was%20my%20most%20anticipated%20ride.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ministry%20of%20Magic%20Interior%20hall%20with%20banners%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682b39c33fe8d39283663421%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20Magic%20felt%20unreal.%3Cp%3EIndia%20Amos%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20a%20huge%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshould-harry-potter-still-be-popular-for-the-next-generation-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHarry%20Potter%20fan%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20grew%20up%20reading%20the%20books%20and%20watching%20the%20movies%2C%20so%20I%20was%20most%20excited%20about%20the%20Battle%20at%20the%20Ministry%20ride.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20to%20get%20to%20the%20screen-based%20ride%2C%20guests%20go%20through%20a%20%26quot%3BFloo%26quot%3B%20(a%20magical%20transportation%20system%20in%20the%20wizarding%20world)%20station%20from%201920s%20France%20to%20contemporary%20London.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20there%2C%20I%20got%20into%20one%20of%20the%20most%20visually%20stimulating%20queues%20I've%20ever%20seen.%20I%20felt%20like%20I'd%20been%20transported%20into%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Magic%20from%20the%20Harry%20Potter%20movies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20the%20single-rider%20line%20I%20was%20in%20bypassed%20several%20of%20the%20themed%20areas%20of%20the%20queue.%20The%20parts%20I%20did%20see%20were%20spectacular%2C%20though.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20in%20all%2C%20I%20waited%20in%20line%20for%20three%20hours.%20The%20ride%20itself%20was%20exciting%20and%20filled%20with%20recognizable%20characters.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20felt%20like%20a%20great%20nod%20to%20the%20Harry%20Potter%20world%2C%20but%20I%20wouldn't%20wait%20so%20long%20to%20ride%20it%20again%20unless%20I%20could%20be%20more%20fully%20immersed%20in%20the%20queue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESuper%20Nintendo%20World%2