sinsider.com%2Fmore-people-receiving-at-home-medical-care-during-the-pandemic-2020-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehospital-at-home%20care%20during%20the%20pandemic%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Stansell%2C%20his%20cofounder%20Connor%20Hailey%2C%20and%20some%20of%20Stansell's%20former%20Uber%20colleagues%20set%20out%20to%20create%20the%20same%20intelligence%20infrastructure%20for%20healthcare%20that%20the%20gig%20economy%20had%20built%20for%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Axle%20Health%20has%20raised%20a%20%2410%20million%20Series%20A%20led%20by%20F-Prime%20Capital%2C%20Business%20Insider%20has%20learned%20exclusively.%20Y%20Combinator%2C%20Pear%20VC%2C%20and%20Lightbank%20also%20participated%20in%20the%20round.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAxle's%20software%20uses%20AI%20to%20handle%20some%20of%20the%20hardest%20problems%20in%20home%20healthcare%3A%20scheduling%2C%20routing%2C%20and%20patient%20engagement.%20Its%20logistics%20engine%20can%20coordinate%20care%20based%20on%20clinical%20eligibility%2C%20patient%20preferences%2C%20clinician%20license%20levels%2C%20and%20even%20cost%2C%20all%20in%20real%20time.%20Its%20customers%20now%20include%20large%20health%20systems%2C%20independent%20home%20health%20agencies%2C%20mobile%20phlebotomy%20providers%2C%20and%20high-acuity%20dispatch%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAxle%20Health%20originally%20set%20out%20to%20be%20a%20home%20health%20provider%2C%20powered%20by%20its%20proprietary%20technology.%20The%20company%20joined%20Y%20Combinator's%20Winter%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E2021%20cohort%20and%20quickly%20scaled%20to%20operate%20in%20all%2050%20states%2C%20growing%20to%20a%20couple%20of%20million%20dollars%20in%20revenue%2C%20Stansell%20said.%20But%20in%202023%2C%20the%20startup%20pivoted%20to%20focus%20on%20building%20and%20licensing%20its%20technology%20for%20other%20hospital-at-home%20providers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20realized%20it's%20better%20for%20us%20%E2%80%94%20and%20better%20for%20the%20industry%20%E2%80%94%20if%20instead%20of%20keeping%20the%20technology%20for%20ourselves%2C%20we%20built%20tools%20to%20empower%20every%20home%20health%20provider%2C%26quot%3B%20Stansell%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAxle%20Health%20announced%20it%20had%20raised%20%244.4%20million%20in%20funding%20in%20February%202024%2C%20which%20Stansell%20said%20included%20seed%20funding%20from%202021%20and%20additional%20funding%20Axle%20raised%20after%20the%20business%20pivoted.%20In%20the%20past%20year%2C%20Stansell%20said%20Axle%20Health%20has%20grown%20its%20revenue%20tenfold.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-fragmented-booming-home-care-industry-caregivers-investors-franchise-owners-2021-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehome%20health%20market%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20growing%20fast%2C%20accelerated%20by%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennials-gen-xers-burdened-long-term-care-costs-for-boomers-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eaging%20population%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20clinician%20shortages%2C%20and%20rising%20consumer%20demand%20for%20in-home%20care.%20Other%20startups%20are%20racing%20to%20meet%20that%20demand%2C%20including%20by%20forging%20ahead%20with%20the%20tech-enabled%20services%20model%20that%20Axle%20shelved%2C%20like%20Sprinter%20Health%2C%20which%20recently%20landed%20a%20%2455%20million%20Series%20B%20led%20by%20General%20Catalyst%20to%20provide%20at-home%20preventive%20care.%20Later-stage%20players%2C%20acute-care%20home%20health%20provider%20DispatchHealth%20and%20home%20care%20tech%20company%20Medically%20Home%2C%20merged%20in%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAxle%20wants%20to%20differentiate%20itself%20both%20by%20plugging%20its%20tech%20into%20the%20existing%20home%20health%20ecosystem%20and%20by%20building%20technology%20that%20clinicians%20actually%20want%20to%20use%2C%20said%20Stansell.%20Axle's%20AI%20generates%20logistics%20plans%20that%20clinicians%20trust%2C%20which%20is%20an%20especially%20difficult%20bar%20to%20clear.%2