%20goal%20is%20really%20to%20position%20itself%20as%20Europe's%20defense%20champion.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20the%20German%20arms%20industry%20needs%20are%20long-term%20contracts%20well%20into%20the%202030s%20and%20state%20subsidies%20to%20rapidly%20scale%20up%20production%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20May%202024%2C%20Germany's%20army%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bundeswehr.de%2Fde%2Fueber-die-bundeswehr%2Fzahlen-daten-fakten%2Fpersonalzahlen-bundeswehr%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBundeswehr%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20180%2C215%20active-duty%20personnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJ%C3%B6rn%20Fleck%2C%20senior%20director%20of%20the%20Atlantic%20Council's%20Europe%20Center%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20a%20targeted%20increase%20of%20the%20German%20armed%20forces%20to%20200%2C000%20had%20been%20delayed%20until%202031%20%26quot%3Bdue%20to%20lackluster%20recruitment%20and%20an%20ageing%20force.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20said%20that%20Germany%20%26quot%3Bhas%20taken%20important%20initial%20steps%20to%20rebuild%20the%20German%20military%20into%20one%20of%20Europe's%20leading%20conventional%20forces.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFleck%20cited%20a%20%E2%82%AC100%20billion%20special%20fund%20to%20modernize%20the%20military%2C%20announced%20in%202022%2C%20and%20constitutional%20changes%20to%20partially%20exempt%20defense%20spending%20from%20Germany's%20debt%20brake%2C%20which%20was%20imposed%20after%20the%202008%20financial%20crisis%20and%20limits%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpikettys-argument-about-greeces-debt-has-three-massive-holes-in-it-2015-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Edeficit%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20just%200.35%25%20of%20GDP.%20By%20contrast%2C%20the%20US%20deficit%20exceeded%206%25%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Fleck%20warned%20that%20Germany%20%26quot%3Bwill%20have%20to%20overcome%20two%20if%20not%20three%20decades%20of%20underinvestment%20in%20its%20armed%20forces.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20resulting%20force%20reductions%2C%20readiness%20problems%2C%20capability%20gaps%2C%20and%20infrastructure%20challenges%20will%20take%20years%20to%20reverse%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BThey%20will%20not%20be%20solved%20by%20money%20alone%20and%20will%20require%20sustained%20political%20will%20and%20leadership.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20positive%20for%20Germany%20is%20its%20thriving%20defense%20industry%2C%20which%20includes%20major%20players%20like%20Rheinmetall%20and%20KNDS%2C%20along%20with%20medium-sized%20companies%20and%20innovative%20startups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202024%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rheinmetall.com%2Fen%2Fmedia%2Fnews-watch%2Fnews%2F2025%2F03%2F2025-03-12-rheinmetall-financial-figures-fical-year-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERheinmetall%3C%2Fa%3E%20saw%20sales%20related%20to%20its%20defense%20business%20increase%20by%2050%25%20year-on-year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGermany's%20defense%20industry%20strategy%2C%20focused%20on%20key%20technologies%2C%20greater%20economies%20of%20scale%2C%20and%20the%20potential%20of%20the%20European%20market%2C%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bpositive%20step%20in%20the%20right%20direction%2C%26quot%3B%20Fleck%20said%2C%20but%20he%20added%20that%20the%20country%20will%20%26quot%3Bhave%20to%20fundamentally%20reform%20its%20procurement%20agency%20and%20processes%26quot%3B%20to%20boost%20its%20defense%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20advancing%20Germany's%20military%20capabilities%20will%20move%20the%20needle%20across%20Europe%2C%20given%20the%20country's%20political%20and%20economic%20weight%20on%20the%20continent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20already%20been%20visible%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20REARM%20initiative%20that%20opened%20the%20door%20for%20countries%20to%20spend%20more%20on%20defense%2C%20and%20the%20proposal%20for%20common%20EU%20borrowing%20to%20fund%20joint%20development%20and%20procurement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20Germany%2C%20Europe's%20reluctant%20hegemon%20with%20its%20fraught%20history%2C%20can%20get%20its%20act%20together%20on%20defense%2C%26quot%3B%20K%C3%BChn%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20can%20others.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcan-germany-build-europe-strongest-military-ukraine-russia-army-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1747911183000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68288f9c68a292900801a109%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcan-germany-build-europe-strongest-military-ukraine-russia-army-2025-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Germany's%20new%20chancellor%20vowed%20to%20build%20Europe's%20strongest%20army%20%E2%80%94%20but%20experts%20say%20underinvestment%2C%20recruitment%2C%20and%20politics%20may%20stand%20in%20the%20way.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22rrommen%40insider.com%20(Rebecca%20Rommen)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A129%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcan-germany-build-europe-strongest-military-ukraine-russia-army-2025-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Periods%20Don%E2%80%99t%20Pause%20During%20Conflict%20%E2%80%94%20With%20Rs%20245%2C%20Help%20Women%20in%20Poonch%20Get%20Reusable%20Pads%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20conflict%20erupts%2C%20headlines%20often%20focus%20on%20the%20immediate%20%E2%80%94%20lives%20lost%2C%20homes%20destroyed%2C%20families%20displaced.%20But%20behind%20each%20of%20these%20headlines%20is%20a%20quieter%20crisis%20that%20rarely%20gets%20spoken%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Poonch%2C%20where%2013%20civilians%20were%20killed%20and%20dozens%20injured%20during%20recent%20shelling%2C%20families%20have%20been%20forced%20to%20flee%20their%20homes.%20In%20such%20moments%2C%20survival%20becomes%20the%20only%20priority.%20Fo