466-50e7-44ca-aafe-dd22964d1659%5C%22%3EOranges%2C%20grapefruit%2C%20and%20fruit%20bowl%20memes%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERichardson%2C%20a%20Marine%20veteran%20who%20attained%20the%20rank%20of%20lieutenant%20colonel%2C%20introduced%20himself%20to%20staff%20members%20on%20May%209%2C%20a%20day%20after%20his%20appointment%2C%20saying%20he%20would%20not%20tolerate%20those%20who%20resisted%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-adopts-elon-musk-plan-cut-government-spending-efficiency-reform-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ereforms%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BObfuscation%2C%20delay%2C%20undermining.%20If%20you're%20one%20of%20those%2020%25%20of%20people%20and%20you%20think%20those%20tactics%20and%20techniques%20are%20going%20to%20help%20you%2C%20they%20will%20not%2C%20because%20I%20will%20run%20right%20over%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20Richardson%20said%20at%20the%20May%209%20meeting.%20%26quot%3BDon't%20get%20in%20my%20way...%20I%20know%20all%20the%20tricks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20town%20hall%20the%20following%20week%2C%20Richardson%20focused%20largely%20on%20conducting%20a%20%26quot%3Bmission%20analysis%26quot%3B%20of%20FEMA's%20operations%20and%20aligning%20with%20Trump%2C%20according%20to%20a%20transcript%20based%20on%20leaked%20audio%20published%20by%20the%20independent%20news%20outlet%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dropsitenews.com%2Fp%2Ffema-david-richardson-leaked-audio%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDrop%20Site%20News%3C%2Fa%3E.%20(Two%20current%20FEMA%20staffers%20confirmed%20to%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20Drop%20Site%20News%20transcription%20of%20the%20meeting%20was%20accurate.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20taking%20questions%20from%20staff%2C%20Richardson%20said%20that%20FEMA%20has%20between%20150%20and%20175%20statutorily%20obligated%20tasks%20to%20conduct%2C%20and%20each%20one%20of%20those%20specified%20tasks%20%26quot%3Bcan%20be%20binned%20into%20categories%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20by%20bin%20them%2C%20I%20mean%20some%20of%20those%2C%20some%20of%20those%20tasks%20will%20be%20kind%20of%20orange-like%20tasks%20%E2%80%94%20and%20by%20orange%2C%20I%20mean%20the%20fruit%20orange%2C%20but%20they%20might%20be%20tangerines%2C%20they%20might%20be%20blood%20oranges%2C%20it%20just%20might%20be%20maybe%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20grapefruit%2C%26quot%3B%20Richardson%20said.%20%26quot%3BAll%20those%20will%20go%20in%20one%20bin.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20FEMA%20staff%20member%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20some%20staffers%20watching%20the%20livestream%20began%20laughing%20during%20the%20remarks%20about%20fruit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20the%20meeting%20concluded%2C%20a%20meme%20of%20Richardson's%20face%2C%20looking%20surprised%2C%20and%20with%20a%20basket%20of%20fruit%20on%20his%20head%2C%20began%20circulating%20among%20FEMA%20employees.%20The%20meme%2C%20shared%20with%20Business%20Insider%20by%20a%20staffer%2C%20was%20styled%20to%20look%20like%20the%20%26quot%3BShrek%202%26quot%3B%20movie%20poster%2C%20with%20the%20title%20%26quot%3BFEMA%202%26quot%3B%20in%20green%20letters%20with%20ogre%20ears.%20Another%20meme%20seen%20by%20Business%20Insider%2C%20which%20was%20styled%20as%20a%20bingo%20card%20for%20people%20listening%20to%20Richardson's%20remarks%2C%20included%20a%20bowl%20of%20fruit%20as%20one%20of%20its%20spaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22107b319e-0024-4470-b161-2c42fc6607c1%5C%22%3E'Texas%20is%20huge!'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20Q%26amp%3BA%20portion%20of%20the%20session%2C%20a%20staff%20member%20asked%20about%20the%20plan%20for%20this%20hurricane%20season%2C%20whether%20the%20agency%20is%20appropriately%20staffed%20for%20emergency%20response%2C%20and%20the%20timeline%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-zers-clean-energy-climate-job-cuts-doge-trump-musk-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etraining%20staff%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20respond.%20Richardson%20said%20the