tainable%2C%20smart%2C%20and%20eco-friendly.%20But%20there%E2%80%99s%20one%20major%20problem%3A%20no%20one%20wants%20to%20buy%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20recycled%20sand%20is%20a%20green%20alternative%2C%20most%20buyers%20still%20prefer%20virgin%20river%20sand%20%E2%80%94%20simply%20because%20it%E2%80%99s%20cheaper.%20While%20river%20sand%20sells%20for%20around%20%E2%82%B92%2C300%20per%20tonne%2C%20people%20are%20only%20willing%20to%20pay%20%E2%82%B9200%20for%20the%20recycled%20version.%20That%E2%80%99s%20a%20massive%20price%20gap%2C%20and%20it%20makes%20it%20tough%20for%20recycling%20businesses%20to%20survive%2C%20let%20alone%20thrive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20irony%20is%20clear%20%E2%80%94%20we%20know%20how%20to%20manage%20waste.%20We%20have%20the%20technology%2C%20the%20infrastructure%2C%20and%20even%20the%20intent.%20But%20unless%20the%20economics%20start%20making%20sense%2C%20many%20of%20these%20promising%20ventures%20will%20continue%20to%20struggle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGovernment%20initiatives%3A%20A%20step%20in%20the%20right%20direction%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20recently%20taken%20some%20major%20steps%20to%20address%20the%20viability%20gap%20in%20waste%20management.%20The%20introduction%20of%20the%20Extended%20Producers%20Responsibility%20(EPR)%20rules%20in%202022%20mandates%20that%20producers%20are%20responsible%20for%20recycling%20a%20percentage%20of%20the%20waste%20they%20generate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20beverage%20companies%20must%20take%20responsibility%20for%20collecting%20and%20recycling%20the%20plastic%20bottles%20they%20use.%20If%20they%20fall%20short%2C%20they%20must%20purchase%20EPR%20certificates%20from%20recycling%20companies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-05-22T083331.113_11zon-1747883027.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22According%20to%20the%20Extended%20Producers%20Responsibility%20(EPR)%20rules%20in%202022%2C%20beverage%20companies%20must%20take%20responsibility%20for%20the%20plastic%20bottles%20they%20use%3B%20Picture%20source%3A%20Unsplash%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-05-22T083331.113_11zon-1747883027.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-05-22T083331.113_11zon-1747883027-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-05-22T083331.113_11zon-1747883027-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-05-22T083331.113_11zon-1747883027-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-05-22T083331.113_11zon-1747883027-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-436476%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Extended%20Producers%20Responsibility%20(EPR)%20rules%20in%202022%2C%20beverage%20companies%20must%20take%20responsibility%20for%20the%20plastic%20bottles%20they%20use%3B%20Picture%20source%3A%20Unsplash%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20opened%20up%20a%20new%20revenue%20stream%20for%20recyclers%2C%20helping%20to%20bridge%20the%20financial%20gap%20and%20making%20their%20operations%20more%20sustainable.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20government%20has%20begun%20mandating%20targets%20for%20producers%20to%20use%20recycled%20materials%2C%20which%20will%20further%20stimulate%20demand%20for%20recycled%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELearning%20from%20Japan%E2%80%99s%20success%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20India%20looks%20to%20improve%20its%20waste%20management%2C%20many%20experts%20say%20Japan%20offers%20a%20great%20example.%20In%20Japan%2C%20it%20all%20starts%20with%20creating%20less%20waste%20and%20designing%20products%20that%20can%20be%20repaired%20and%20reused.%20Nearly%20all%20their%20waste%20is%20collected%20and%20processed%20efficiently%20%E2%80%94%20thanks%20to%20strong%20awareness%20and%20a%20deep-rooted%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F401397%2Fsneakers-kobsook-empowering-differently-abled-designers-aziz-kapapi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eculture%20of%20sustainability%3C%2Fa%3E.%20For%20India%2C%20the%20real%20challenge%20is%20building%20that%20same%20mindset%20and%20making%20eco-friendly%20habits%20a%20part%20of%20daily%20life.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20prime%20example%20of%20this%20is%20the%20resistance%20in%20Kodungaiyur%2C%20North%20Chennai%2C%20where%20residents%20are%20protesting%20the%20establishment%20of%20a%20waste-to-energy%20plant.%20They%20fear%20that%20such%20a%20project%20would%20make%20the%20area%20toxic%2C%20unaware%20that%20modern%20plants%20have%20negligible%20emissions%20compared%20to%20the%20harmful%20effects%20of%20open%20waste%20dumps.%20As%20Aditi%20Ramola%2C%20Technical%20Director%20at%20the%20International%20Solid%20Waste%20Association%20(ISWA)%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EMint%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CLack%20of%20funds%20means%20waste%20takes%20the%20least-cost%20route%20to%20disposal%2C%20which%20is%20being%20dumped%20in%20an%20open%20area%20away%20from%20habitation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20path%20to%20a%20circular%20economy%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20easy%2C%20but%20Hyderabad%20shows%20it%E2%80%99s%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20smart%20investments%2C%20strong%20policies%20like%20EPR%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F385612%2Fdr-naperla-praveen-chittoor-rural-health-educational-society-healthcare-environmental-impact%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epublic%20awareness%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20change%20can%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20waste%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20resource%2C%20not%20a%20burden%2C%20everything%20shifts.%20A%20cleaner%2C%20greener%20future%20is%20within%20reach%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20starts%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Saumya%20Singh%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESource%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Findustry%2Fcircular-economy-hyderabad-re-sustainability-kkr-jamnagar-gujarat-recycle-biogas-organic-waste-carbon-footprint-landfill-11747042996593.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3DSummary%2Cmunicipal%2520solid%2520waste%2520every%2520year%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHow%20Hyderabad%20tamed%20its%20mountain%20of%20waste%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20N%20Madhavan%20for%20Mint%2C%2012%20May%202025%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%22%2C%22published%22%3A1747897945000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Finfosys-ad-banner-1746535509.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D435634%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hyderabad's%20waste%20crisis%20once%20mirrored%20that%20of%20many%20Indian%20cities%2C%20but%20today%2C%20it%20tells%20a%20different%20story.%20Discover%20how%2