eila-badyari-castelino-inspirational-journalist-mother-stories%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20joy%20of%20motherhood%3C%2Fa%3E%20wrestled%20from%20her%20thrice%2C%20naturally%2C%20she%20was%20sceptical%20the%20fourth%20time%20around.%20%E2%80%9CBeing%20cautiously%20happy%20became%20our%20acquired%20philosophy%20of%20life.%20When%20we%20announced%20this%20pregnancy%2C%20the%20immediate%20reaction%20from%20people%20was%20%E2%80%98oh%20wow%2C%20you%20guys%20must%20be%20on%20top%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20my%20husband%20would%20reply%20that%20we%2C%20as%20a%20couple%2C%20were%20being%20cautiously%20happy.%20It%20became%20our%20joint%20mantra%20to%20deal%20with%20what%20was%20to%20come%20after%20what%20we%20had%20endured.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20get%20complacent%20with%20luck.%20%E2%80%9CSo%20many%20expecting%20mothers%20who%20face%20miscarriage%2C%20infertility%2C%20and%20high-risk%20pregnancies%20feel%20joy%20when%20they%20get%20pregnant.%20But%20they%20also%20end%20up%20being%20very%20protective%20of%20this%20happiness.%E2%80%9D%20This%20prudent%20manoeuvring%20around%20happiness%20became%20palpable%20during%20moments%20like%20planning%20a%20baby%20shower.%20%E2%80%9CShould%20we%3F%20Should%20we%20not%3F%20Should%20we%20celebrate%3F%20When%20should%20we%20break%20the%20news%20to%20people%3F%20Should%20we%20start%20getting%20the%20nursery%20ready%3F%20Should%20we%20buy%20things%20for%20the%20baby%3F%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20decision%20was%20a%20conundrum.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDid%20Radhika%20lean%20into%20the%20side%20of%20hope%20or%20not%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20soon%20figured%2C%20hope%20is%20a%20capricious%20dynamic.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNot%20every%20day%20was%20the%20same.%20You%20can%20only%20hold%20on%20to%20hope%20and%20faith%2C%20and%20believe%20that%20things%20will%20be%20okay%2C%20but%20there%20are%20moments%20when%20you%20doubt%20it.%20There%20was%20major%20coexistence%20of%20joy%20and%20fear%20in%20my%20life%20at%20that%20point%2C%20because%20we%20never%20knew%20what%20the%20next%20stage%20would%20hold.%20At%20every%20stage%2C%20there%20were%20so%20many%20fears%20we%20dealt%20with.%20We%20would%20often%20wonder%20whether%20the%20next%20ultrasound%20would%20be%20fine%20or%20reveal%20something.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERadhika%E2%80%99s%20fear%20was%20realised%20when%2C%20after%20one%20particular%2020-week%20ultrasound%2C%20the%20doctor%20informed%20her%20that%20the%20foetus%20had%20a%20short%20nasal%20bone%2C%20which%20could%20be%20suggestive%20of%20Down%E2%80%99s%20Syndrome.%20%E2%80%9CShould%20the%20test%20come%20positive%2C%20I%20was%20recommended%20not%20to%20proceed%20with%20the%20pregnancy.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20test%20was%20negative.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnxiety%20revisited%20her%20once%20more%20when%20she%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20gestational%20diabetes.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20levels%20were%20impossible.%20So%20from%20a%20person%20who%20feared%20needles%2C%20I%20became%20someone%20who%20would%20prick%20myself%20multiple%20times%20every%20day.%E2%80%9D%20The%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F241496%2Fdiabetes-diabetic-meals-gluten-free-diet-fixx-kolkata-surojit-rout-ipshita-banerjee-food-home-cooks-geriatric-delivery-start-up-order-online-subscription-model-vid01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ediabetes%20also%20necessitated%20a%20complete%20overhaul%20of%20her%20diet%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20to%20control%20my%20portions%2C%20control%20my%20rice%20intake%2C%20carbohydrate%20intake%2C%20and%20increase%20my%20protein%20intake.%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20sugar%20in%20my%20tea%2C%20no%20biscuits%2C%20no%20bread%2C%20all%20of%20the%20things%20I%20love%2C%20so%20that%20was%20also%