n%20officially%20selected%20for%20the%202025%20New%20York%20Indian%20Film%20Festival%20and%20the%202024%20Rome%20Short%20Film%20Festival.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20day%2C%20I%20reached%20out%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2F_neelsoni%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENeel%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20invited%20him%20for%20a%20candid%20interview%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fem%3E.%20He%20joined%20in%20along%20with%20his%20film%20editor%2C%20Shubika%20Sharma%2C%20and%20his%20aunt%2C%20Ayesha%20Grewal%2C%20to%20share%20more%20about%20his%20journey%20%E2%80%94%20and%20what%20drove%20him%20to%20explore%20such%20sensitive%2C%20often%20overlooked%20themes%20in%20his%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFinding%20a%20calling%20in%20the%20forests%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20spoke%2C%20what%20stayed%20with%20me%20was%20just%20how%20personal%20this%20film%20is%20to%20Neel%20%E2%80%94%20not%20only%20as%20a%20filmmaker%2C%20but%20as%20someone%20shaped%20by%20the%20layered%2C%20often%20unseen%20stories%20surrounding%20him%20growing%20up.%20%3Cem%3EBabli%20by%20Night%20%3C%2Fem%3Eisn%E2%80%99t%20just%20a%20documentary.%20For%20Neel%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20way%20of%20honouring%20a%20life%20that%20might%20have%20otherwise%20gone%20unnoticed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20introduced%20to%20the%20forests%20when%20I%20was%20nine%20years%20old%20by%20my%20%3Cem%3EMaasi%20(maternal%20aunt)%3C%2Fem%3E.%20I%20eventually%20picked%20up%20the%20camera%20and%20started%20taking%20photographs.%20But%20after%20some%20time%2C%20photography%20saturated%20me%20and%20I%20yearned%20to%20disco