0Industry.%20As%20we%20spoke%2C%20he%20said%20something%20that%20struck%20a%20chord%3A%20%E2%80%9CIndia%E2%80%99s%20growth%20story%20is%20full%20of%20opportunities%20for%20the%20world.%E2%80%9D%20That%20line%20perfectly%20captured%20the%20energy%20in%20the%20room.%20This%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20about%20trade%E2%80%94it%20was%20about%20creating%20an%20economic%20corridor%20that%20connects%20continents%20through%20shared%20values%3A%20climate%20resilience%2C%20digital%20innovation%2C%20and%20inclusive%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-20T192519.382_11zon-1747749352.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr.%20Ashish%20Sharma%20with%20Hon.%20Shri%20Piyush%20Goyal%2C%20Union%20Minister%20of%20Commerce%20%26amp%3B%20Industry%2C%20at%20the%20India-Mediterranean%20Business%20Conclave%202024%2C%20discussing%20India%E2%80%99s%20role%20in%20building%20sustainable%2C%20strategic%20economic%20corridors.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-20T192519.382_11zon-1747749352.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-20T192519.382_11zon-1747749352-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-20T192519.382_11zon-1747749352-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-20T192519.382_11zon-1747749352-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-20T192519.382_11zon-1747749352-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-435418%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr.%20Ashish%20Sharma%20with%20Hon.%20Shri%20Piyush%20Goyal%2C%20Union%20Minister%20of%20Commerce%20%26amp%3B%20Industry%2C%20at%20the%20India-Mediterranean%20Business%20Conclave%202024%2C%20discussing%20India%E2%80%99s%20role%20in%20building%20sustainable%2C%20strategic%20economic%20corridors.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20India-Mediterranean%20Business%20Corridor%20(IMBC)%20aims%20to%20transform%20connectivity%20through%20a%20number%20of%20strategic%20thrusts%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHigh-capacity%20digital%20infrastructure%2C%20such%20as%20Reliance%E2%80%99s%20India-Europe%20subsea%20cable%3B%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EClean%20energy%20partnerships%2C%20especially%20in%20green%20hydrogen%20and%20blue%20economy%20sectors%3B%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECollaboration%20on%20Industry%204.0%20technologies%2C%20with%20innovation%20hubs%20like%20Marseille%20and%20Indian%20tech%20cities%3B%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPort-led%20development%20and%20maritime%20logistics%2C%20including%20alignment%20with%20India%E2%80%99s%20Sagarmala%20initiative%3B%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EUrban%20sustainability%20and%20smart%20manufacturing%2C%20backed%20by%20deeper%20people-to-people%20and%20research%20linkages.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20framing%20the%20IMBC%20as%20a%20bridge%20across%20Europe%2C%20Africa%2C%20and%20South%20Asia%2C%20India%20is%20catalysing%20a%20new%20model%20of%20corridor-led%20cooperation.%20A%20model%20that%20is%20not%20just%20economically%20viable%20but%20also%20climate-conscious%20and%20innovation-forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBIMSTEC%3A%20Strengthening%20Eastern%20Regionalism%20for%20Shared%20Resilience%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20Confederation%20of%20Indian%20Industry%E2%80%99s%20BIMSTEC%20Business%20Summit%202024%2C%20I%20had%20the%20opportunity%20to%20engage%20with%20high-level%20delegations%20from%20member%20countries%2C%20discussing%20the%20vital%20role%20of%20regional%20collaboration%20in%20addressing%20shared%20challenges.%20Climate%20change%20mitigation%2C%20adaptation%2C%20and%20environmental%20sustainability%20are%20now%20fundamental%20pillars%20within%20BIMSTEC%E2%80%99s%20evolving%20framework%2C%20reflecting%20the%20urgent%20need%20for%20cooperative%20solutions%20across%20borders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bay%20of%20Bengal%20Initiative%20for%20Multi-Sectoral%20Technical%20and%20Economic%20Cooperation%20(BIMSTEC)%2C%20comprising%20Bangladesh%2C%20Bhutan%2C%20India%2C%20Myanmar%2C%20Nepal%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20and%20Thailand%20%E2%80%93%20is%20emerging%20as%20a%20key%20platform%20for%20regional%20economic%20integration%20with%20sustainability%20at%20its%20core.%20At%20the%202024%20BIMSTEC%20Business%20Summit%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20eastern%20engagement%20took%20center%20stage%20as%20member%20nations%20underscored%20their%20collective%20commitment%20to%20climate%20resilience%2C%20clean%20technology%20collaboration%2C%20and%20inclusive%20development%20across%20one%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20most%20climate-vulnerable%20regions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20green%20trade%20facilitation%20and%20eco-tourism%20infrastructure%20to%20nanotech%20for%20clean%20water%20and%20climate%20policy%20coordination%2C%20BIMSTEC%20is%20aligning%20economic%20integration%20with%20environmental%20stewardship.%20As%20one%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20most%20climate-vulnerable%20regions%2C%20this%20collaboration%20offers%20a%20powerful%20model%20for%20shared%20resilience%2C%20knowledge%20exchange%2C%20and%20inclusive%2C%20low-carbon%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20region%20highly%20vulnerable%20to%20climate%20impacts%20such%20as%20rising%20sea%20levels%2C%20extreme%20weather%20events%2C%20and%20biodiversity%20loss%2C%20BIMSTEC%20offers%20a%20platform%20to%20synchronise%20policies%2C%20mobilise%20resources%2C%20and%20share%20knowledge%2C%20strengthening%20col